name: Original Art: OhNO Panda watercolor
description:
FRAMED original watercolor art done on archival acid free watercolor paper.

Total frame size = 9" x 9"  art is roughly  6"x 6"

Who is OhNo? OhNo is an original character based on my son and his antics. He wears different costumes based on his mood. Why OhNo? One thing my son use to love to do when he was a toddler was pick up something around the house, smash it to the ground, and then say "Oh No". -Good Times.

name: OhNo with Stache - Letterpress & Screened combo print
description:
Letterpress/Screenprint combination print. Limited Edition of 80 signed and numbered by the artist. (UnFramed)

These prints are 2 color Letterpress printed with a metallic bronze ink screen printed mustache over top. Printed on heavy #140 lb Muscletone Madero Beach stock by French Paper Co.

Standard 8x10 size for easy framing.

name: OhNo with Stache Letterpress print variations
description:
Letterpress print. Limited Edition of only 4 of each of these extra color combinations signed and numbered by the artist. (UnFramed)

These prints are 3 color Letterpress printed with a metallic silver ink for the mustache. Printed on heavy #140 lb Muscletone Hot Fudge, Pink Lemonade, or Kraft paper stock by French Paper Co.

Standard 8 x 10 size for easy framing.

name: Original art. OhNo Floats, Screen print on wood panel + FRAMED
description:
• 18 x 24 Framed
• Only 4 made!
• Signed and numbered
• Hand Screened onto wood panel by artist. 

4 custom mixed colors hand pulled onto the wood. The best thing is seeing that wood grain show through which gives the art another sense of depth.

Who is OhNo? OhNo is an original character based on my son and his antics. He wears different costumes based on his mood. Why OhNo? One thing my son use to love to do when he was a toddler was pick up something around the house, smash it to the ground, and then say "Oh No". -Good Times.

Mounting hardware on back for easy hang.
This piece also has a careful treatment of a UV resistant coating of acrylic matte varnish.

The piece will be shipped via USPS and includes insurance and tracking if located within the United States.

name: Hand Screen Printed Poster: OhNo Floats, unframed
description:
"OhNo Floats" Hand pulled original art screen print.
• Limited Edition of only 22 prints 
• Signed and numbered
• 18 x 24 
• Screen Printed on heavy French Construction: Whitewash 100# Cover stock

Each print is unique. All 4 colors were custom mixed on this print and have been hand pulled by the artist one at a time. This process which includes some slight imperfections give each piece character and make them a one of a kind piece of art. Think Andy Warhol -that's screen printing.
